dct_title_s: Khanate of Khiva after Russian sources, by Major Herbert Wood, R.E.
dct_description_sm: Lower Amu Darya and delta, southern Aral Sea, dry lake and river beds, and areas inundated during floods are shown. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Figures in decimal feet denote heights above Aral. Towns and built areas in Amu Darya Valley are shown. From: Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 45 (1875), pp. 367-413; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687
